12:59.612 --> 13:02.449
Truly, just divine.

13:02.482 --> 13:04.284
Was that gerbil?

13:04.317 --> 13:07.320
I like to please my husband.
(sultry chuckle)

13:07.354 --> 13:08.989
You know what I was thinking?

13:09.022 --> 13:11.491
