into the bedroom.

13:14.627 --> 13:17.865
(laughs)
Honey... the crumbs.

13:17.898 --> 13:19.166
Oh, but it's pudding.

13:19.199 --> 13:20.834
Oh, my gosh, uh...

13:20.868 --> 13:22.602
I am such a ninny.

13:22.635 --> 13:25.205
