and society was telling me

13:39.486 --> 13:41.488
I was no longer a sexual being.

13:41.521 --> 13:42.789
Screw them.

13:42.822 --> 13:45.225
I learned my erotic
essence didn't die

13:45.258 --> 13:46.626
just because my marriage did.

13:46.659 --> 13:49.029
That thing between your legs

13:49.062 --> 13:51.698
only turns into an elbow
if you let it.

13:53.666 --> 13:57.337
