importantly, to this baby,

14:49.990 --> 14:51.724
to work out our
differences,

14:51.758 --> 14:53.526
so let's just
cut the sarcasm

14:53.560 --> 14:56.463
and have an honest conversation
about our feelings.

14:56.496 --> 14:57.697
