14:57.730 --> 14:59.766
You over-share
and you suck the air

14:59.799 --> 15:01.201
out of every room
you walk into.

15:01.234 --> 15:02.535
News flash, Bryan:

15:02.569 --> 15:06.806
You are a self-absorbed,
insecure smug little princess.

15:06.839 --> 15:08.075
