15:08.108 --> 15:09.876
'cause that's exactly
what I was going for.

15:09.909 --> 15:11.878
(laughs)
I should've known
you weren't mature enough

15:11.911 --> 15:13.413
to have a real
communication.

15:13.446 --> 15:14.881
Oh! Oh, I'm not mature?

15:14.914 --> 15:17.217
